channel.title: I have no NPCSpawning.java file
channel.description:
Hello everybody, i am trying to move some shops over to Edgeville, now is my only problem that i really have no idea how to do this. I read some guides and i think i need a NPCspawning.java file but i can't find mine.. Will someone please help me? Thank you.
#SOLUTION FOUND: https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=538900.0#

item.title: I have no NPCSpawning.java file
item.dc:creator: @Kidpaparoach Kidpaparoach
item.description:
@Kidpaparoach wrote:

Assuming your using Pi do this…

Stand directly above an npc that is spawned in edgeville, type in ::mypos then in the search bar when you open up your source either type in the x-axis coords or the y-axis coords then search through the files till you find the correct one.
